      "role": "user",
      "content": "10k sounds more manageable i guess. but i've seen some people in wellness forums saying that doing much higher hits like 50k for just 10 days is a common way to \"recharge\" your system when you're super deficient. if i do that, would it actually be dangerous or is it just people being overly cautious? im really trying to get my energy back fast.",
